pan><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">38元</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">/片</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">哈德逊全抛釉地砖</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal\\\\\">HDPY20ABC</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">和田黄玉系列价格：</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">79元</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">/片</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">哈德逊</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal\\\\\">普拉提</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">地砖</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal\\\\\">AP060121云瑞莎贝拉</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal\\\\\">系列价格：</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">45元</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">/片</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">地砖按材质可分为釉面砖、通体砖、抛光砖、玻化砖等，花色和品种多样，选用地砖时要</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">与</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">整体居室设计风格</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">相协调</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">，才能起到装饰作用。地砖的规格有很多，常见的有600*600、800*800等，铺设地点不同需要的规格不同，地砖价格也有很大差别。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.